1955;;The Last Command;;American;;Frank Lloyd;;Sterling Hayden, Anna Maria Alberghetti, Ernest Borgnine;;war, western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Last_Command_(1955_film);;In 1835, Jim Bowie realizes that there were uneasy disputes between the Mexican government and the American immigrants who've settled in Texas. Dozens of American men, including Stephen Austin have been arrested for supposedly igniting rebellions against the Mexican governor Juan Almonte and the Mexican garrisons throughout Texas.